actions.message:
===USER COMMANDS===

?doge - see nintendo's latest game. ( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°)

?gasp - see a gasping cat.

?ping - pong.

?avatar - Get someone's avatar. (Usage: ?avatar @example)

?website - Get the link to the Wiiverse Website.

===ADMIN COMMANDS===

?kick - Kick the mentioned user from the server. (Usage: ?kick @example)

?ban - Ban the mentioned user from the server. (Usage: ?ban @example)

?unban - Unban the mentioned user from the server. (Usage: ?unban @example)

actions.message:
Welcome to the Wiiverse Discord Server!
Here are some rules for the Discord Server.

Rules: 

1. Be nice; no curse words and no cyber-bullying!
2. No NSFW content! (Porn, Gore, Futanari, etc.)
3. No personal information!
4. No racism toward any religion or race!
5. No plagiarism in any way shape or form! (taking someone's project, text, images, etc.)
6. No Spamming! Spamming is forbidden!
7. No raiding the server!!!!1!!!11!!!!1!!  I mean, all haters would ignore this, right? :thinking:
8. No advertising unless in #self-promotion!(edited)
9. No Political Topics
10. If you're admin, DO NOT ENABLE NSFW WITH SHEEPBOT
11. No bot spam! We have already had this recently.
12. You aren't able to get the role Beta Testers anymore. It was only for the first 10 people who joined.
13. Sending TTS messages are disabled, because members get annoyed by the sound that it creates.
14. You are not allowed to mention everyone, because some members dislike getting pingged.
15. No trolling, its annoying and can result in a ban.
